OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny heavy
OL,6,Fshowers will tend to die out this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee further showers develop across
OL,9,Fwestern areas, but generally drier
OL,10,Faround the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,15,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,16,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
