OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,6,Fcloud developing on Sunday alongside
OL,7,Frisk of showers later. A few showers
OL,8,Fon Monday but mostly dry by Tuesday.
OL,9,FWinds lighter than of late.
